author: Charles Creitz
title: Gaetz calls for end to NIH grant to Wuhan virology lab, says it can be done with 'stroke of a pen'
description: Rep. Matt Gaetz, R-Fla., called on Health & Human Services Secretary Alex Azar Tuesday to cease funding a research grant to the Wuhan Institute of Virology in China, telling "Tucker Carlson Tonight" the action could be accomplished "with the stroke of a pen."
